  "texts": [
    "There is also fare-well ceremony for AI pets: When Sony announced in 2014 that they would no longer support updates for AIBO, the community of owners began sharing tips on providing care for their digital friends in the absence of official support.",
    "Winky is a play-bot produced by the company Mainbot and comes equipped with a microphone, sensors, a speaker, LEDs, a rotating head and ears, a motion and distance detector, and a gyroscope for interacting with the environment.",
    "12 Replika is a generative AI chatbot that was released to the public in 2017 and within 1 year was used by 2 million people.",
    "The user must answer a series of questions to create a network that serves as contextual frame for the \"friendship\"-including romantic and, before the function was disabled by the developers in 2023, erotic relationships.",
    "lives, sometimes even because they can share with the x-bot something they would never address in relation to people."
  ]
}